}}}} As prime minister, he has received [[Opinion polling on the Narendra Modi premiership|consistently high approval ratings]] within India. Modi has been described as engineering a political realignment towards [[right-wing politics]]. He remains a highly controversial figure domestically and internationally over his Hindu nationalist beliefs and handling of the Gujarat riots, which have been cited as evidence of a majoritarian and exclusionary social agenda.{{efn|Sources discussing the controversy surrounding Modi:<br />{{bulleted list
